      "content": "it's just getting so hard lately. i feel like i'm just a weight on everyone's shoulders. my kids, they're so busy with their own lives and here i am... just needing more and more help for things i used to do myself. i don't want to be a nuisance to them anymore. i just feel like i've lived my part and it's okay to just... stop, isn't it?",
